OL,3,CIdris Elba says he was never going to
OL,4,Cbe James Bond and 007 should not be
OL,5,C'woke'
OL,7,FSir Idris Elba has said James Bond
OL,8,Fshould not be made "woke" and that
OL,9,Frumours he was set to play 007 were
OL,10,F"not realistic".
OL,12,FThe award-winning actor, known for
OL,13,FLuther and The Wire, was rumoured to
OL,14,Fbe in the running to play the beloved
OL,15,Fcharacter for more than a decade,
OL,16,Fhowever, Sir Idris said it was "never
OL,17,Flegit".
