OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780945878
OL,3,CIdris Elba says he was never going to
OL,4,Cbe James Bond and 007 should not be
OL,5,C'woke'
OL,7,FThe 53-year old said the character was
OL,8,F"written how he was written for a
OL,9,Freason" and that not all audiences
OL,10,F"will go" for a black Bond because it
OL,11,Fis "not what they like in their
OL,12,Fculture".
OL,14,FSpeaking to British GQ, Sir Idris
OL,15,Fsaid: "It was never legit. It was
OL,16,Falways just a rumour. I've always felt
OL,17,Fthat it's not a realistic thing.
OL,19,F"James Bond was written how he was
OL,20,Fwritten for a reason. But I was
OL,21,Fcomplimented by it.
