OL,3,CIdris Elba says he was never going to
OL,4,Cbe James Bond and 007 should not be
OL,5,C'woke'
OL,7,F"In realistic terms, some markets just
OL,8,Fdon't go for that.
OL,10,F"Bond is big all over the world and
OL,11,F(audiences) won't (all) go for a black
OL,12,Fmale, an African male, playing Bond.
OL,14,F"That's not what they like in their
OL,15,Fculture. Period."
