OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780945878
OL,3,CIdris Elba says he was never going to
OL,4,Cbe James Bond and 007 should not be
OL,5,C'woke'
OL,7,FSir Idris added that some reality
OL,8,Fchecks are needed for the franchise
OL,9,Fbut changing Bond is not something he
OL,10,Fthinks is necessary.
OL,12,F"Bond is so unrealistic, so a hint of
OL,13,Freality is good, but let's not try and
OL,14,Fmake it woke. I think you've got to be
OL,15,Fpure to what it is: escapism.
OL,17,F"Don't try and answer the world's
OL,18,Ftaste. Just be Bond," he added.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOUzD@UO]
