OL,3,CIdris Elba says he was never going to
OL,4,Cbe James Bond and 007 should not be
OL,5,C'woke'
OL,7,FElba was knighted last week by the
OL,8,FKing after being recognised in the New
OL,9,FYear Honours for services to young
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FIn 2022, the 53-year-old founded the
OL,13,FElba Hope Foundation, which supports
OL,14,Fcommunity empowerment, education,
OL,15,Fyouth advocacy and sustainable
OL,16,Fdevelopment.
