OL,3,CIdris Elba says he was never going to
OL,4,Cbe James Bond and 007 should not be
OL,5,C'woke'
OL,7,F007 was previously portrayed by
OL,8,FEnglish actor Daniel Craig, who took
OL,9,Fon the role in 2006's Casino Royale
OL,10,Fand starred in five films until he
OL,11,Fleft the franchise with 2021's No Time
OL,12,FTo Die.
OL,14,FSince then, there has been a lot of
OL,15,Fspeculation surrounding who will play
OL,16,Fthe next 007, with some raising
OL,17,Fconcerns that he would not be British
OL,18,Fafter Amazon MGM Studios took creative
OL,19,Fcontrol of the franchise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
