OL,3,CIdris Elba says he was never going to
OL,4,Cbe James Bond and 007 should not be
OL,5,C'woke'
OL,7,FIt was announced in August last year
OL,8,Fthat the next film will be written by
OL,9,FPeaky Blinders creator Steven Knight.
OL,11,FCasting for the next Bond reportedly
OL,12,Fbegan last month with a number of
OL,13,Fstars rumoured to be up for the role
OL,14,Fincluding Masters of the Air actor
OL,15,FCallum Turner, Wuthering Heights star
OL,16,FJacob Elordi and Baby Girl actor
OL,17,FHarris Dickinson.
